Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 21/06/2025
App Name: Archipel
Contact: archipelltd@gmail.com

Archipel respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.

1. Camera Permission
Our app requests access to your device’s camera:

To allow you to take photos for features such as profile pictures or content uploads.

Camera access is only used when you explicitly open a feature that requires it.

We do not record, store, or share camera content without your action.

2. Data Usage
We do not collect or store any personal data unless you choose to provide it (e.g., uploading a photo). Any photos taken using the app may be:

 Uploaded securely to our server.

We do not share your information with third parties.

3. Data Security
We take appropriate security measures to protect your data. No method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, but we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your information.

4. Children’s Privacy
Our app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

5. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. We will notify you of changes by updating this page with a new "Effective Date".

6. Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:


archipelltd@gmail.com
